<div class="calendaria chat-release">
  <div class="release-header">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar"></i>
    <strong>{{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.Title" version=version}}</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="release-body">
    <p class="release-patreon">
      <strong><a href="https://www.patreon.com/3deathsaves" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-patreon"></i> Now on Patreon!</a></strong>
    </p>

    <h4>Breaking Changes</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Calendaria now requires Foundry VTT v14</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>New Features</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Cinematic time skips can trigger by the hour and show an animated clock</li>
      <li>Each scene can override how Calendaria tints lighting, weather, and moons</li>
      <li>Event reminders can be set in hours, days, weeks, months, or years</li>
      <li>Weather effects can render under tiles or the map foreground, switch on only in the dark, and stay on chosen
        map levels</li>
      <li>Weather presets can keep their color without darkening the scene</li>
    </ul>

  </div>

  <a class="open-note" href="{{repoUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> {{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.ReleaseNotes"}}
  </a>
</div>
